# Exception: the scanner's .env.production contains ONLY public values
# (Supabase URL + anon key + store_id — all designed to be safe in client
# bundles). It must be committed so the Docker build can bake them in.
# Service-role keys and other secrets NEVER go here — they live in fly secrets.
!apps/scanner/.env.production
supabase/.temp/
supabase/.branches/
tmp/data/

# Locally-trusted dev TLS certs (mkcert) — never commit private keys
*.pem
*-key.pem
